    },
    {
      "point": "Introduction of a large-scale, novel dataset (WebBrain-Raw)",
      "evidence": "A substantial dataset is created from Wikipedia articles and their references, which is ten times larger than prior comparable datasets... The scale of the dataset (10x larger than WikiSum) is itself a significant methodological contribution."
    },
    {
      "point": "Superior performance against strong baselines",
      "evidence": "ReGen consistently outperforms all baselines across automatic metrics and human evaluations... ReGen significantly outperforms GPT-3 (text-davinci-002) on BLEU, METEOR, and ROUGE metrics."
