    },
    {
      "point": "Underspecified methodological details for dataset construction",
      "evidence": "Crucial details regarding the construction of the 'WebBrain-Raw' dataset, particularly the definition and application of the 'term recall metric ($P_{ST}$)'... are missing or underspecified."
